imdb.plot outline: "The Duchamps School of Acting" follows Jonathan Duchamps and his class of dedicated acting students as they work to develop their talents, and master Jonathan's technique. Eccentric and passionate, Jonathan's approach to his craft is by turns intense and ridiculous. The documentary explores the relationships between teacher to student and artist to mentor. How far will someone go for what they love... what wouldn't you do to achieve your dreams?
imdb.title: The DuChamps School of Acting
plot: Jonathan Duchamps has been teaching for over ten years. His passion and dedication has inspired many of his students. This documentary follows several of those students as they grapple with the challenges of becoming an honest to god actor.::Jordan Dibe

"The Duchamps School of Acting" follows Jonathan Duchamps and his class of dedicated acting students as they work to develop their talents, and master Jonathan's technique. Eccentric and passionate, Jonathan's approach to his craft is by turns intense and ridiculous. The documentary explores the relationships between teacher to student and artist to mentor. How far will someone go for what they love... what wouldn't you do to achieve your dreams?::Jordan Dibe
